    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH predictions demonstrate mean error of 9.3% against experimental data, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all 5 evaluated operating points.",
